msgstr "KDE kopiena, Felipe Kinoshita"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.licentia.metainfo.xml:14
msgid ""
"Licentia helps you choose a license for your project, it allows you to check "
"the license's permissions, conditions and limitations, how to add said "
"license to your project and read the full license."
msgstr ""
"„Licentia“ palīdz izvēlēties licenci jūsu projektam. Šī programma ļauj "
"apskatīties licences atļaujas, noteikumus un ierobežojumus, kā arī norāda, "
"kā pievienot minēto licenci projektam un ļauj iepazīties ar pilnu licences "
"tekstu."

